  <entry>
    <title>Insecure/STARTTLS/SSLTLS 测试邮箱搭建</title>
    <url>/2021/02/20/insecurestarttlsssltls-ce-shi-you-xiang-da-jian/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h3 id="安装Hmailserver-https-www-hmailserver-com-需要提前安装-netformwork；"><a href="#安装Hmailserver-https-www-hmailserver-com-需要提前安装-netformwork；" class="headerlink" title="安装Hmailserver(https://www.hmailserver.com/), 需要提前安装.netformwork；"></a>安装Hmailserver(<a href="https://www.hmailserver.com/">https://www.hmailserver.com/</a>), 需要提前安装.netformwork；</h3><h3 id="按照提示设置密码；"><a href="#按照提示设置密码；" class="headerlink" title="按照提示设置密码；"></a>按照提示设置密码；</h3><h3 id="使用hMailServer-Administrator连接到hmailserver-密码是安装的时候设置的；"><a href="#使用hMailServer-Administrator连接到hmailserver-密码是安装的时候设置的；" class="headerlink" title="使用hMailServer Administrator连接到hmailserver, 密码是安装的时候设置的；"></a>使用hMailServer Administrator连接到hmailserver, 密码是安装的时候设置的；</h3><h3 id="首先添加一个domain；"><a href="#首先添加一个domain；" class="headerlink" title="首先添加一个domain；"></a>首先添加一个domain；</h3><h3 id="接着添加几个账号，设置好密码；"><a href="#接着添加几个账号，设置好密码；" class="headerlink" title="接着添加几个账号，设置好密码；"></a>接着添加几个账号，设置好密码；</h3><h3 id="生成测试证书，可以去https-myssl-com-create-test-cert-html"><a href="#生成测试证书，可以去https-myssl-com-create-test-cert-html" class="headerlink" title="生成测试证书，可以去https://myssl.com/create_test_cert.html"></a>生成测试证书，可以去<a href="https://myssl.com/create_test_cert.html">https://myssl.com/create_test_cert.html</a></h3><h3 id="可以看到以下三个文件："><a href="#可以看到以下三个文件：" class="headerlink" title="可以看到以下三个文件："></a>可以看到以下三个文件：</h3><p>cert.pem对应服务器证书<br>full_chain.pem对应CA证书<br>private.key对应私钥</p>
<h3 id="回到hMailServer-Administrator-打开Settings-gt-Advanced-gt-SSL-certificates；"><a href="#回到hMailServer-Administrator-打开Settings-gt-Advanced-gt-SSL-certificates；" class="headerlink" title="回到hMailServer Administrator, 打开Settings-&gt;Advanced-&gt;SSL certificates；"></a>回到hMailServer Administrator, 打开Settings-&gt;Advanced-&gt;SSL certificates；</h3><h3 id="点Add-新加一个证书；"><a href="#点Add-新加一个证书；" class="headerlink" title="点Add 新加一个证书；"></a>点Add 新加一个证书；</h3><h3 id="给证书起一个名字，Certificate-file-对应cert-pem，Private-key-file对应private-key；"><a href="#给证书起一个名字，Certificate-file-对应cert-pem，Private-key-file对应private-key；" class="headerlink" title="给证书起一个名字，Certificate file 对应cert.pem，Private key file对应private.key；"></a>给证书起一个名字，Certificate file 对应cert.pem，Private key file对应private.key；</h3><h3 id="然后保存即可；"><a href="#然后保存即可；" class="headerlink" title="然后保存即可；"></a>然后保存即可；</h3><h3 id="切换到Settings-gt-Advanced-gt-TCP-ports"><a href="#切换到Settings-gt-Advanced-gt-TCP-ports" class="headerlink" title="切换到Settings-&gt;Advanced-&gt;TCP ports;"></a>切换到Settings-&gt;Advanced-&gt;TCP ports;</h3><h3 id="这里可以按照需要进行设置相应的端口"><a href="#这里可以按照需要进行设置相应的端口" class="headerlink" title="这里可以按照需要进行设置相应的端口:"></a>这里可以按照需要进行设置相应的端口:</h3><p>一般对应如下:<br>SMTP: 25(Insecure)/587(STARTTLS)/465(SSLTLS).<br>POP3: 110<br>IMAP:143</p>
<h3 id="对于测试部分，这里只是用到了SMTP的发送功能，收件功能没有特殊要求。"><a href="#对于测试部分，这里只是用到了SMTP的发送功能，收件功能没有特殊要求。" class="headerlink" title="对于测试部分，这里只是用到了SMTP的发送功能，收件功能没有特殊要求。"></a>对于测试部分，这里只是用到了SMTP的发送功能，收件功能没有特殊要求。</h3><h3 id="选中0-0-0-0-587-SMTP-Connection-security-选择-STARTTLS-Required-SSL-Certificate选择步骤10里面的证书，-然后保存，这样就配置好了STARTTLS"><a href="#选中0-0-0-0-587-SMTP-Connection-security-选择-STARTTLS-Required-SSL-Certificate选择步骤10里面的证书，-然后保存，这样就配置好了STARTTLS" class="headerlink" title="选中0.0.0.0/587/SMTP, Connection security 选择 STARTTLS(Required), SSL Certificate选择步骤10里面的证书， 然后保存，这样就配置好了STARTTLS;"></a>选中0.0.0.0/587/SMTP, Connection security 选择 STARTTLS(Required), SSL Certificate选择步骤10里面的证书， 然后保存，这样就配置好了STARTTLS;</h3><h3 id="同样，选中0-0-0-0-465-SMTP-如果没有参考PORT-25来配置一个就好-，Connection-security-选择SSL-TLS-SSL-Certificate选择步骤10里面的证书然后保存，这样就配置好了SSL-TLS；"><a href="#同样，选中0-0-0-0-465-SMTP-如果没有参考PORT-25来配置一个就好-，Connection-security-选择SSL-TLS-SSL-Certificate选择步骤10里面的证书然后保存，这样就配置好了SSL-TLS；" class="headerlink" title="同样，选中0.0.0.0/465/SMTP(如果没有参考PORT 25来配置一个就好)，Connection security 选择SSL/TLS, SSL Certificate选择步骤10里面的证书然后保存，这样就配置好了SSL/TLS；"></a>同样，选中0.0.0.0/465/SMTP(如果没有参考PORT 25来配置一个就好)，Connection security 选择SSL/TLS, SSL Certificate选择步骤10里面的证书然后保存，这样就配置好了SSL/TLS；</h3><h3 id="到此，邮件服务器就已经配置完成；"><a href="#到此，邮件服务器就已经配置完成；" class="headerlink" title="到此，邮件服务器就已经配置完成；"></a>到此，邮件服务器就已经配置完成；</h3><h3 id="使用邮件客户端进行测试，可以用thunderbird-或者foxmail"><a href="#使用邮件客户端进行测试，可以用thunderbird-或者foxmail" class="headerlink" title="使用邮件客户端进行测试，可以用thunderbird 或者foxmail;"></a>使用邮件客户端进行测试，可以用thunderbird 或者foxmail;</h3><h3 id="分别指定不同的SMTP发送服务器设置；"><a href="#分别指定不同的SMTP发送服务器设置；" class="headerlink" title="分别指定不同的SMTP发送服务器设置；"></a>分别指定不同的SMTP发送服务器设置；</h3><h3 id="确保可以收到邮件；"><a href="#确保可以收到邮件；" class="headerlink" title="确保可以收到邮件；"></a>确保可以收到邮件；</h3><h3 id="检查hMailSever的log，可以看到对应的加密log"><a href="#检查hMailSever的log，可以看到对应的加密log" class="headerlink" title="检查hMailSever的log，可以看到对应的加密log:"></a>检查hMailSever的log，可以看到对应的加密log:</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">`<span class="string">&quot;TCPIP&quot;</span>            916      <span class="string">&quot;2021-02-18 13:44:22.844&quot;</span>     <span class="string">&quot;TCP - 10.245.17.234 connected to 10.245.47.36:588.&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;DEBUG&quot;</span>          916      <span class="string">&quot;2021-02-18 13:44:22.844&quot;</span>     <span class="string">&quot;TCP connection started for session 163&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;SMTPD&quot;</span>          916      163      <span class="string">&quot;2021-02-18 13:44:22.860&quot;</span>     <span class="string">&quot;10.245.17.234&quot;</span>           <span class="string">&quot;SENT: 220 DCG-L3-C2--09-L ESMTP&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;SMTPD&quot;</span>          6528    163      <span class="string">&quot;2021-02-18 13:44:22.860&quot;</span>     <span class="string">&quot;10.245.17.234&quot;</span>           <span class="string">&quot;RECEIVED: EHLO BMC&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;SMTPD&quot;</span>          6528    163      <span class="string">&quot;2021-02-18 13:44:22.860&quot;</span>     <span class="string">&quot;10.245.17.234&quot;</span>           <span class="string">&quot;SENT: 250-DCG-L3-C2--09-L[nl]250-SIZE 20480000[nl]250-STARTTLS[nl]250-AUTH LOGIN PLAIN[nl]250 HELP&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;SMTPD&quot;</span>          916      163      <span class="string">&quot;2021-02-18 13:44:22.860&quot;</span>     <span class="string">&quot;10.245.17.234&quot;</span>           <span class="string">&quot;RECEIVED: STARTTLS&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;SMTPD&quot;</span>          916      163      <span class="string">&quot;2021-02-18 13:44:22.860&quot;</span>     <span class="string">&quot;10.245.17.234&quot;</span>           <span class="string">&quot;SENT: 220 Ready to start TLS&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;DEBUG&quot;</span>          4348    <span class="string">&quot;2021-02-18 13:44:22.860&quot;</span>     <span class="string">&quot;Performing SSL/TLS handshake for session 163. Verify certificate: False&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;TCPIP&quot;</span>            4348    <span class="string">&quot;2021-02-18 13:44:23.391&quot;</span>     <span class="string">&quot;TCPConnection - TLS/SSL handshake completed. Session Id: 163, Remote IP: 10.245.17.234, Version: TLSv1.2, Cipher: ECDHE-RSA-AES256-GCM-SHA384, Bits: 256&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;TCPIP&quot;</span>            2300    <span class="string">&quot;2021-02-18 13:36:26.688&quot;</span>     <span class="string">&quot;TCP - 10.245.17.234 connected to 10.245.47.36:466.&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;DEBUG&quot;</span>          2300    <span class="string">&quot;2021-02-18 13:36:26.688&quot;</span>     <span class="string">&quot;TCP connection started for session 90&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;DEBUG&quot;</span>          2300    <span class="string">&quot;2021-02-18 13:36:26.688&quot;</span>     <span class="string">&quot;Performing SSL/TLS handshake for session 90. Verify certificate: False&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;TCPIP&quot;</span>            2300    <span class="string">&quot;2021-02-18 13:36:26.969&quot;</span>     <span class="string">&quot;TCPConnection - TLS/SSL handshake completed. Session Id: 90, Remote IP: 10.245.17.234, Version: TLSv1.2, Cipher: ECDHE-RSA-AES256-GCM-SHA384, Bits: 256&quot;</span>`</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
